Subject: [PATCH 3/624] save transcript to logs/transcripts/first-pass.jsonl

Add a verbatim JSONL copy of the agent/chat transcript to
logs/transcripts/first-pass.jsonl so the conversation history is
preserved alongside the repository. This file records the prior session
(the Cursor parent agent transcript) in the project's logs/transcripts
directory for auditing and replay.

Changes:
- Create logs/transcripts/first-pass.jsonl containing the conversation JSONL entries extracted from the session.

Why: The transcript was requested to be stored in the repository logs so
the project's agent activity and decisions (subagent dispatches, plan
updates, and debugging steps) are captured for traceability and future
debugging.
